{"tid":1626294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[可能係核彈] 有做生意既review保單","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:52:40.000Z","uid":220942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e72fc0ce5c6cee4a0e23e5eb6f82dc37fec69d1a","tid":1626294,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"今日超市便利店全線分店都close<br />\n<br />\n其實係好怪，偏遠既細分店照計點都冇影響。但就5點close, 好有伏味。<br />\n我估計係政府放風俾保險業界，同商鋪講某段期間冇得保，例如包括水火保，員工保。<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果各位自己做生意或者朋友做生意，不妨叫保險公司review公司保險。叫保險公司𨤳清有關或將會有關問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n臨市政府 = 叛亂/內亂/不合法, 影子政府 = 痴線/合法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624793</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"03b13964adaa1e3f49eb3de3895f9a5bb6380184","tid":1626294,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a810f80a0db449ff3517f383e71f931e8cea7fb8","tid":1626294,"uid":99532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"幫推無壞"},{"pid":"4dee91d0fdb81e9cde4a9071000ea0e4e7f5444b","tid":1626294,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a810f80a0db449ff3517f383e71f931e8cea7fb8","tid":1626294,"uid":99532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"幫推無壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"謝<br />\n<br />\n保險公司一唔受保，外資就要走<br />\n<br />\n到時唔受宣布戒嚴都已經好大動盪"},{"pid":"7402deb87790d156c1aa0557de4b5a302ffde872","tid":1626294,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de8ecb71297e3b6cd2061960a593017eeda0dcc","tid":1626294,"uid":145418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-